Class X509CertificateAuthenticationTokenTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cesecore.authentication.tokens.X509CertificateAuthenticationTokenTest
  • public class X509CertificateAuthenticationTokenTest
extends Object
    Unit tests for the X509CertificateAuthenticationToken class. Note that this test class subverts the unit test concept slightly by using 'real' certificates.
    Version:
